channel.title: The Rookie (Halo Toymation) - Vote for my friends video please!
channel.description:
So my buddy on another forum made an entry for the Mega Bloks Halo Toymation contest and he did an amazing job with it. So please, check it out and vote for his video if you like it. You can vote once per day until October 16th if you want to be really helpful.
Its something of a parody of Halo 3: ODST
[url]https://halotoymation.megabloks.com/videos/3078-The-Rookie[/url]
btw the creator of the video is GeneticSpartan, which you may or may not have heard of if you enjoy Halo machinima. Here is his youtube channel for those interested. [url]https://www.youtube.com/user/GeneticSpartan[/url]
